  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "I think the mev-boost timeout toward the relays should be slightly less than what [consensus clients apply](https://github.com/ethereum/builder-specs/blob/main/specs/validator.md#constants) to mev-boost, to give some time to mev-boost to select the bid and respond within `1s`, otherwise the entire bid selection will be discarded and CL will fallback to local EL if one of the relays responds in >1s.\r\n\r\n",
