    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "Also adding different flags for registerValidator and getPayload timeout, which are allowed to take longer. \r\n\r\nThat would be useful in particular for anyone running many validators but having a bad internet connection. We have previously seen requests from India in particularly bad circumstances taking 2.5 seconds to transmit 1k validator registrations (which is only ~500kb).\r\n",
